FBIS4-38400 "drsov104_f_94015" FBIS-SOV-94-104 Daily Report 30 May 1994 National Affairs Fault at Nuclear Power Plant Corrected Fault at Nuclear Power Plant Corrected LD3005181694 Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service in Ukrainian 1600 GMT 30 May 94 LD3005181694 Kiev Radio Ukraine World Service Ukrainian BFN [Text] The generator of power unit No. 1 at Khmelnitskiy nuclear plant was disconnected for several hours. The plant information center reports that this was caused by false activation of the modular transformer containment system due to a short circuit in the control cable conductors. The generating set was reconnected upon the removal of the defect. The conditions of the plant's safe operation were not affected. The radiation situation is unchanged.
